                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='59250' id='14' type-v2='text' w='12400' x='86800' y='7500'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' italic='true' underline='true'>KEY INSIGHTS</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontsize='10'>• </run>
                    <run>Experience level is the primary driver of salary, with senior roles earning ~50% more than mid-level roles
• Cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP) are central to high-paying AI roles
• Individual skills have limited salary impact at senior level—skill combinations matter more
• High-demand roles require integrated skill stacks, particularly in cloud and machine learning ecosystems</run>
                  </formatted-text>
